{
  "stem": "21527.1",
  "chunk_idx": 9,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 4.5,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And, [PAUSES FOR 5 SECONDS] and that's how we spent our time.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "I had some friends in the flats.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And that's how we lived.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And at any time, the Germans could just march in to your place and take whatever they wanted to or take away people that they thought looked like they were subversive or something.",
      "word_count": 33
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "So we really didn't know from one moment to another what was going to happen to us.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Yes, in the street.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And I also remember a couple of Germans coming into our home and admiring some of the beautiful things that we still had from way back.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "But whether they actually took something or not, I can't remember.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Yes.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Well, there was a curfew.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And there wasn't much food.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "The curfew-- we weren't allowed out after a certain time in the street.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "So every evening-- people had to do something in the evening-- so people in our-- in our flat used to get together and play cards, or talk, or have little soirees, a bit of music.",
      "word_count": 35
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "They just had to somehow entertain each other, because otherwise, you could just go crazy thinking of what would happen.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "At some stage in the ghetto, rumors started that some of the other ghettos in Poland were being liquidated and that people were being taken to concentration camps and what the concentration camps were like.",
      "word_count": 35
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And I'm not sure whether there were rumors of ovens in, in-- when we were in the ghetto, but there was a fear that this was only a temporary measure, that the Germans really had plans to annihilate all the Jewish population of Poland.",
      "word_count": 44
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Could be.",
      "word_count": 2
    }
  ],
